data.description: ** $5,000 Buyer incentives and REDUCED!** Make your next move to COUNRY WALK! This home is located in a beautiful and quiet neighborhood just outside of St. Augustine which makes it the perfect location to be close to shopping, dining and downtown while being tucked away from the hustle and bustle.  Country Walk is also only 5 minutes to I95 for easy commuting. This 3/2 with 2 car garage will be perfect for the first time home buyer, growing family, or retiree wanting to live in a quiet, friendly neighborhood. This home is wired for ADT security, NEST thermostat, and also has installed sprinklers and whole house water filter. The kitchen has granite counters, and tall upper cabinets. There is a brand new washer and dryer in the laundry room, and the owners even made the attic a perfect place for storage! Make your appointment today!  Home is being sold AS-IS as current owner is being deployed and will be out of country.
